<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Time for a Test</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Time for a Test</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The good thing about Smalltalk is that it&apos;s really easy to test things quickly. Why don&apos;t we create an instance of </text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">Animal</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and see what we can do with it so far. In a workspace evaluate:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">myAnimal := Animal new. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">&quot;Display the following&quot;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">myAnimal name.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">&quot;Now give it a name&quot;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">myAnimal name: &apos;Dog&apos;.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">&quot;And display the name again&quot;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">myAnimal name.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">These simple tests show how we can create a new instance of an </text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">Animal</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, assign a name to it and then query the name again. </text></para>
  </body>
